snippet.title: OpenSpades Trailer
snippet.description:
OpenSpades is a client for the Voxlap game Ace of Spades 0.75, which is a free multiplayer game created by Ben Aksoy. 

DOWNLOAD HERE: https://github.com/yvt/openspades/releases/

OpenSpades by http://yvt.jp/

Ace of Spades0.75: http://buildandshoot.com/downloads.php

Song: Born to conquer by Phil Rey
